rc=\"https://na.cx/i/nYgHxM8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnYgHxM8.png&h=4d504f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5P2fSNa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5P2fSNa.png&h=169d1075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCCI係根據正式買賣合約註冊數據計算，CCL則純屬中原喺未有正式數據前「領先估計」嘅數字。<br />\n<br />\n請睇番以下CCL喺今年一月份「領先估計」當月嘅指數，平均約為175.98<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fuQQGFB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfuQQGFB.png&h=5f5f008d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但琴日公布嘅CCI，一月份指數實際上只有173.67，兩者相差達2.31個百分點。樓市實際上係跌，但CCL就呃你係升。報紙地產版永遠只會報導「靠估」嘅CCL，但唔會報導較準確嘅CCI，亦唔會講畀你知CCL其實成日「估」大咗條數，所以你以為樓市升緊，實際上係跌緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:01:19.000Z","msg":"on9仔<br />\n你自己睇下兩個指數既走勢係咪一致啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXbz85e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXbz85e.jpg&h=627dbed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ncci用註冊資料 ccl用中原自己成交既資料，上得註冊處 都慢中原成交 3至4星期   cci數據有滯後係好正常<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncci一月註冊咪大約等於12月ccl成交，12月ccl同11月ccl比咪一樣都係跌<br />\n2020/12/21 - 2020/12/27  176.22 <br />\n<br />\n 2020/11/30 - 2020/12/06 177.75<br />\n姐係話12月ccl既成交（等於cci1月上註冊處）比11月（等於12月上註冊處）跌0.86%，跌得仲多過cci<br />\n0.79%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家滯後既係cci，咁ccl係咪比cci先反映近況呀 掉返轉黎講咪你依啲on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd151b56510b6d13f766416fe41a2142c301f71","tid":2452402,"uid":209830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:06:03.000Z","msg":"畀咗票先 畀咗票再慢慢諗都唔遲"},{"pid":"c679ad47e1d70721b9c288870de06a89dbcc1c18","tid":2452402,"uid":205377,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7ac12877edeca8e72d85c9136ee549a9134731b7","tid":2452402,"uid":182608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:51:30.000Z","msg":"我最鍾意幫你地呢D年青人上車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:08:36.00